    <div class="tab-pane" id="tab6">
      In Polytene, in similarity to GitlabCI, exists Runner object. Runner do the job. If you want to make everything up and running, follow this steps:
      <ul>
        <li>Create Runner object in Polytene panel.</li>
        <li>Pick source code of PolyteneRunner from Github and install it on separate machine according to the manual.</li>
        <li>While configuring installed PolyteneRunner use generated private token from created in Polytene Runner object.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

